question: Went to my doctors appt on Wednesday 12/2 at 10:30. My doctor found protein in my urine and my blood pressure was up just a little bit. So she sent me to the hospital to get tested for preeclampsia. My daughters heart rate was dropping so my doctor decide to do a emergency c-section. Scariest thing ever. I had my daughter December 2 at 12:35pm. I was 37 weeks. She weighed 5pds 1oz.
